kpi.name: M386B2C12

kpi_info.title: Average call setup time of the failed call setup attempts
kpi_info.use: The average call setup time of the failed call setup attempts, which terminated in the normal release (where the clear code is in the range of 001-3FF). The unit of the average call setup time in ASCII report is seconds, in XML reports, it is 10 milliseconds.

kpi.kpi_alias: Average call setup time of the failed call setup attempts
